VITÓRIA
Paulo Musse; Moura, Flávio, Marcone and Leandro; Pingo, Claiton, 
Fernando (Xavier) and Juninho Petrolina (Felipe); Artur (Mateus) and Cláudio.
Coach: Arturzinho

BAHIA
Emerson; Clebson, Jean, Valder and Jefferson; Reginaldo Nascimento 
(Valdomiro), Bebeto Campos, Luís Carlos Capixaba (Carlos Alberto) and Paulo 
César (Curê); Marcos Paulo and Uéslei.
Coach: Evaristo de Macedo.

Venue: Manoel Barradas (Barradão), in Salvador
Referee: Paulo César Oliveira
Goals: Juninho Petrolina, Fernando and Cláudio (Vitória); Marcone (own goal)
(Bahia)



Topscorers:     Uéslei (Bahia), 19 goals
                Cláudio (Vitória), 8 goals
                Marcos Chaves (Camaçari), 8 goals




